# Netscape HTTP Cookie File
# https://curl.se/docs/http-cookies.html
#
# This is an example file. Replace with your own cookies.
# Use the `videodl generate-cookies` command or `videodl browser-login <url>`
# to generate cookies automatically.
#
# Format: domain	flag	path	secure	expiry	name	value
#
# Example:
# .example.com	TRUE	/	TRUE	1893456000	session_id	your_session_token_here
# .example.com	TRUE	/	TRUE	1893456000	auth_token	your_auth_token_here
